[
  {
    "text": "AH!  Too Sexy!!!",
    "start": 13.68,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Captain Roll!",
    "start": 14.86,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "He has a biological weapon!",
    "start": 26.84,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm on it!",
    "start": 28.1,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "No need!",
    "start": 29.54,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I have successfully apprehended the suspect.",
    "start": 30.04,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Vision!  You're here!",
    "start": 32.28,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Of coarse I am.  Why wouldn't I be?",
    "start": 33.68,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "The Avengers are dangerous.",
    "start": 37.28,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "You have unlimited power and no supervision.",
    "start": 38.8,
    "duration": 2.68
  },
  {
    "text": "You realize the earth was under attack right?",
    "start": 41.48,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "That footage is us saving the day.",
    "start": 43.58,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "People die when you \"save the day\".",
    "start": 45.76,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Didn't you guys fire a nuke at the city when the Chitauri showed up?",
    "start": 48.08,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!  They did!  I was there!  \nExactly!",
    "start": 51.2,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah what was that gonna do?  \nShower New York with hugs?",
    "start": 52.36,
    "duration": 2.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Be serious.",
    "start": 55.06,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "We need to be put in check guys.",
    "start": 55.86,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "We?!",
    "start": 57.98,
    "duration": 0.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Tony, you're the one who's reckless!",
    "start": 58.6,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Cough!  You made Ultron. Cough!",
    "start": 60.42,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone else in this room...\njust stopping evil",
    "start": 62.32,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "The U.N. doesn't see it that way.",
    "start": 65.08,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Well tell the U.N. Vision picked up Thor's hammer.",
    "start": 66.64,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "So we're pretty sure we've been doing the right thing up to this point.",
    "start": 68.94,
    "duration": 2.84
  },
  {
    "text": "I DID lift the hammer!",
    "start": 71.78,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Just stopping evil.",
    "start": 73.38,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what I'm saying.",
    "start": 74.74,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "What happens if we don't sign it?",
    "start": 75.52,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Then consider yourselves retired.",
    "start": 77.68,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Ha ha ha ha!\nThat's crazy!",
    "start": 79.86,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "That wont last for five minutes.\nJokes are fun.",
    "start": 81.58,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "He he he.\nLet me help you out.",
    "start": 82.96,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Here just cross out the title.",
    "start": 84.48,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Make it say the \"TONY\" accords...",
    "start": 86.26,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "And we'll all sign right now.",
    "start": 88.84,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Deal.",
    "start": 92.04,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 92.6,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "When you can do the things that I can",
    "start": 94.84,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "but you don't",
    "start": 97.64,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "and then the bad things happen",
    "start": 98.78,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "They happen because of you.",
    "start": 101.58,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "No.  That's not it.",
    "start": 103.88,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not?",
    "start": 105.16,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "That's not the line.",
    "start": 105.8,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on.  Say it right.",
    "start": 106.66,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "What line?",
    "start": 108.1,
    "duration": 0.68
  },
  {
    "text": "You know.",
    "start": 109.0,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "With...",
    "start": 111.8,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "great power comes...",
    "start": 112.8,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "great responsibility?",
    "start": 114.02,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "There it is!",
    "start": 115.66,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "They're not stopping!",
    "start": 120.98,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Alright then...",
    "start": 122.5,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Web'em up.",
    "start": 123.38,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Aaaagh it's so sticky!",
    "start": 127.02,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Hmm.  Great job kid!",
    "start": 128.9,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Get to the quinjet in the hanger, Buck!",
    "start": 130.58,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "We're almost there!",
    "start": 133.14,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "AHAA!  I'm Gi-ANT-Man!",
    "start": 134.42,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "*gasp*\nSomething just flew in me!",
    "start": 137.42,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Vision!",
    "start": 142.74,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, man!",
    "start": 143.54,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Screams*",
    "start": 146.4,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Give me vitals!",
    "start": 150.48,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh he's dead!",
    "start": 151.52,
    "duration": 0.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Rhooooooodes!",
    "start": 152.34,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't bull crap me, Rogers.  Did you know?",
    "start": 157.48,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes.",
    "start": 161.06,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Tank missile!",
    "start": 162.66,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry, Tony.",
    "start": 164.44,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I know what I did.",
    "start": 167.28,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I know I hurt you.",
    "start": 169.68,
    "duration": 1.58
  },
  {
    "text": "But I want YOU to know...",
    "start": 172.2,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry.",
    "start": 174.54,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't get to be sorry!",
    "start": 175.26,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "You're right!",
    "start": 176.72,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't deserve to live.",
    "start": 177.64,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Bucky that's not true!",
    "start": 178.92,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "What you did...",
    "start": 180.08,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "It wasn't you.",
    "start": 181.04,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I can speak for myself, Steve!  Gah!",
    "start": 182.0,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "I did those things!",
    "start": 184.76,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "and I accept responsibility.",
    "start": 186.62,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "But I AM sorry.",
    "start": 190.08,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "*sigh*\nGet'm out of there!",
    "start": 197.86,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go",
    "start": 199.4,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Nooooo!",
    "start": 200.18,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "You were supposed to collapse from the inside!",
    "start": 201.1,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "I was lucky enough that Stark even showed up at the same time as you to watch this video!",
    "start": 203.56,
    "duration": 3.86
  },
  {
    "text": "And now you're totally foiling my plans!",
    "start": 207.5,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on!",
    "start": 210.4,
    "duration": 0.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Stay down.",
    "start": 213.52,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Final warning.",
    "start": 214.92,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I could do this all d..",
    "start": 215.96,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Aaaagh!",
    "start": 216.84,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "La la la la Not listening!",
    "start": 232.44,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Not listening!",
    "start": 234.72,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Can't hear you!",
    "start": 236.02,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "fingers in my ears",
    "start": 237.28,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Hands are free!",
    "start": 237.98,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Simply, I CAN'T HEAR YOOOOOOU!",
    "start": 239.62,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry.",
    "start": 243.68,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Where you saying something?",
    "start": 244.4,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Nooooo!",
    "start": 245.9,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "*captain tackle*",
    "start": 246.62,
    "duration": 0.56
  },
  {
    "text": "And so...",
    "start": 248.68,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "We caught Zemo...",
    "start": 249.32,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Found out he was the real person who bombed the U.N...",
    "start": 250.24,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "And we NEVER went to Siberia.",
    "start": 252.48,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "What was in Siberia?",
    "start": 254.4,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh... who knows.",
    "start": 255.64,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep!  Whoooo knows.",
    "start": 256.94,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Well that sounds kind of anticlimactic.",
    "start": 258.96,
    "duration": 2.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I was kind of hoping you guys would fight each other or something.",
    "start": 261.46,
    "duration": 2.68
  },
  {
    "text": "You know!  The whole \"choose a side\" trend.",
    "start": 264.14,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh we're still split.",
    "start": 266.62,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Tony's still assembling his team.",
    "start": 267.92,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh we've already assembled!",
    "start": 269.66,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Team Iron Man's where it's at, baby!",
    "start": 271.7,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Any of you jokers wanna join?",
    "start": 274.1,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "We've even got our own Batman and Superman!",
    "start": 275.6,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I believe I would prefer to be on team...",
    "start": 277.84,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Captain America.",
    "start": 280.84,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "What?!",
    "start": 282.1,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought you were all about the accords!",
    "start": 282.6,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Nobody is about the accords, Tony!",
    "start": 284.42,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Not even you!",
    "start": 286.72,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!  You'll sneak behind their back the second you need something without their consent.",
    "start": 287.52,
    "duration": 4.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah but...",
    "start": 291.78,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "We've got Spider-Man!",
    "start": 292.58,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Mr. Stark, I'm really excited to be here but I gotta ask you a question...",
    "start": 293.86,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you gonna date my aunt?",
    "start": 297.08,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Because I don't know if I'm ready for you to be my...",
    "start": 299.0,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "My Dad-Uncle.",
    "start": 301.42,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Now now.  Let's not get ahead of ourselves.",
    "start": 302.38,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh Okay... My bad.",
    "start": 304.36,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Is he even old enough to vote?",
    "start": 305.5,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "He's old enough to steal that mighty shield!",
    "start": 306.9,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "And you know what that means!",
    "start": 308.76,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Sooooooo",
    "start": 310.42,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Unless you're a plane!",
    "start": 311.34,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Or a bomb!",
    "start": 312.38,
    "duration": 0.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Or some ice!",
    "start": 313.0,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Or a brain washed buddy!",
    "start": 313.6,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Or a Spider-Man!",
    "start": 314.9,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Then you don't necessarily have to yield!",
    "start": 316.72,
    "duration": 4.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Please stop for the LOVE OF GOD!",
    "start": 321.14,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh.  Never would've guessed.",
    "start": 323.14,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Cap hates music.",
    "start": 324.84,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you?  Hydra or something?",
    "start": 325.88,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "NO!",
    "start": 327.3,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Why would.. Why would you think that?!",
    "start": 328.28,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Well B.P.  if you're not with us, then I believe your seat is over there.",
    "start": 330.46,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "This seems very childish.",
    "start": 333.94,
    "duration": 1.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep.",
    "start": 335.52,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Move.",
    "start": 337.62,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Or you will be moved.",
    "start": 338.14,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Not a chance Cat-Man",
    "start": 339.68,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you know why?",
    "start": 341.24,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Why?",
    "start": 342.38,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Because I'm BATMAN!",
    "start": 342.88,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh my gosh!  He can have my seat!",
    "start": 344.0,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "This is getting too crowded anyway.",
    "start": 345.5,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooooooh!  Thank God!",
    "start": 347.18,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought he was never gonna move!",
    "start": 350.1,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "How long have you been there?",
    "start": 351.96,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I have seen things!",
    "start": 353.58,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes.  I am Zemo.",
    "start": 380.26,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "You're probably wondering why I've brought you here.",
    "start": 381.22,
    "duration": 2.18
  },
  {
    "text": "It is... not to make you fight, but...",
    "start": 383.84,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "to...",
    "start": 386.46,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "KISS!",
    "start": 387.56,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "*smooches*",
    "start": 389.14,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Heehee",
    "start": 391.34,
    "duration": 0.5
  }
]